Package: hockeystick
Title: Download and Visualize Essential Climate Change Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Hernando",
           family = "Cortina",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "hch@alum.mit.edu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6790-4870"))
Description: hockeystick provides easy access to essential Climate Change datasets to non-climate experts. Users can download the latest raw data from authoritative sources and view it via pre-defined ggplot2 charts. Datasets include atmospheric CO2, instrumental and ice-core temperature records, sea levels, and Arctic/Antarctic sea-ice.
